<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"> 
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="description" content="Nexa Tokens and NFT Viewer">
    <meta name="web" content="https://ntviewer.netlify.app">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/ico" sizes="32x32" href="img/favicon.ico">
    <title>Nexa Tokens Viewer</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha256-wLz3iY/cO4e6vKZ4zRmo4+9XDpMcgKOvv/zEU3OMlRo=" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha256-m81NDyncZVbr7v9E6qCWXwx/cwjuWDlHCMzi9pjMobA=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@3.6.3/dist/jquery.min.js" integrity="sha256-pvPw+upLPUjgMXY0G+8O0xUf+/Im1MZjXxxgOcBQBXU=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </head>

  <body class="container bg-dark text-white">

    <div style="text-align:center">
      <p></p>
      <h1><img src="./img/nexalogo.png" alt="BCH" width="100"> Nexa Tokens and NFTs Viewer (demo)</h1>
      <p></p>
      <br>

      <div class="card text-dark">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h5>View tokens and NFTs created on the <a href="https://nexa.org">Nexa</a> (proof-of-work) blockchain</h5>
          <p><i>We use electrum-cash rostrum server method to get data from the blockchain</i></p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-title">Group Id (token Id) examples:</p>
          <p class="card-text">
            nexa:trs2ccuvqmf62853mwt7ly478qkhjugrk92kfl6cf75yk8hssyqqqlcpr87w8<br>
            nexa:tpnl45e72t6lsdnkdzzrs0xk7w59vp0plkw6wtey03hlca2mvcqqqj9vxsmc0<br>
            nexa:tz0ptps4cu5m32lltm9v974wlgz5tf7j0z8dd5xd7unxdupghvqqq5zrm4pd0<br>
            nexa:tz40uzgq0q3j42388rsjjm8w2y66kc49yc4d5d3rfwma0q8q0vqqqj9fj3guu<br>
            nexa:tqqqr08dpmzdmqvx2ggdwpsxspfsfn32e8yxc70yu5xxmsatagqqqdt2z8shv<br>
            nexa:tqeu5wmfcymm0taasw5cwapcht9ch3faj0qkus6zu7smmdfnxqqqqpzgvqhsg<br>
            nexa:tp7ex7wn5sgtjwm3veptgxcjagxgd9tj4cp7z4p8uxxaku0dusqqqkm0v97dc<br>
          </p><br>
          <form action="/" method="post">
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="tokenid" placeholder="Group Id (token Id) e.g. nexa:tz0ptps4cu5m32lltm9v974wlgz5tf7j0z8dd5xd7unxdupghvqqq5zrm4pd0"><br>
            <input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" value="View token or NFT"><br>
          </form>
          <br>
          <p><img src="<%= tokenimage %>" width="300"></p>
          <br>
          <p><%= content %></p>
          <p><%= error %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>  
    <p></p>
    <br><br>

    <div style="text-align:center">  
      <footer style="font-size: 14px;">
        <p><a href="https://t.me/mazetokens"><img src="./img/telegram.png" alt="Telegram" width="32"></a>
          <a href="https://github.com/mazetoken/nexatokens"><img src="./img/github.png" alt="Github" width="32"></a>
        </p>
      </footer>
      <br>
    </div>

    <script type="application/json" src="server.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>